ore obscure, shine </div><div class="t m2cb x8d h2d y47b ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">out as the noonday.&quot; No man can think </div><div class="t m41f x8d h2d y672 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the thoughts of God, unless he walks in the </div><div class="t m31b x8d h2d y3b0 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ways of God. </div><div class="t mb96 x94 h2d y13eb ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">THE &quot; sure word of prophecy &quot; tells us </div><div class="t me99 x8d h2d y1323 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">again and again that this earth shall be de- • </div><div class="t m14b xc6 h2d y32a ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">stroyed by fire, and that in that fire the un- </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
